caeser1:

    getMode() - > encrypt || decrypt hiihiin garaas avah function

    getMessage() -> garaas e || d hiih message iig avna

    getKey() -> e || d hiih key iig garaas avna

    getTranslatedMessage() -> mode 'd' bwal key sorog utgatai bolgono encrypt hiigdsen
    ->  message-iin useg bolgonii ord() function-s irj baigaa int utgaas hasaj decrypt hiisne message garna
    ->  herev e bwal ascii code deer key iin utgiig nemj encrypt hiine

caeser2:
    caeser_encrypt() -> realtext -iig ogogdson step utgaar nmegduulj encrypt hiij baigaa function
    -> ingehdee realtext-iin temdeg bureer guine. Temdeg uppercase, eswel lowercase-d baigaag
    -> uppercase, lowercase 2 massiviin alind baigaagaar ni medne.
    -> tged massive-iin taarch baigaa index deer step iin utgaa ned 26-d uldegteltei huwaana.
    -> uchir ni step utgaar nemehed 26 buyu tsagaan tolgoin hemjeenees hetreh ucir.
    -> Suuld outText-iig butsaana.

